Installation

Put into your Gemfile:

gem "crowd_authentication", :git => git@github.com:arvatoSystemsNA/crowd_authentication.git

Usage

If you are using Rails 2 you have to include CrowdAuthentication::Controller in your ApplicationController.

Use method authenticate_with_crowd_id(crowd_id, password) in your controllers for authentication. This method returns true if authentication using given crowd id and password was successful and false otherwise.